</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eifsgl epDHtf pf-92_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-93_">Integrate inclusive family policies</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-95_">Track and promote paternity leave usage</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-97_">Support fathers’ mental health initiatives</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-99_">Build recognition programmes that honour all employees’ contributions, at work and at home.</li></ul><p class="sc-EROOM ZMPII pf-101_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-9e625bce-6321-4967-9607-d07b16dd989f"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><em><strong>Last updated on&nbsp;14-06-2025</strong></em></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-d79e" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dJjagV cQqdEF pf-179_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-kCMLfs khbiTF"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-137_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bkSTSn hpQOMO pf-138_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-gvZzpm chTUkt pf-139_ pf-heading-1-h3 _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmzxHC hSXinz pf-141_">About the author
